        <div id="page-intro">
            <h1>Publish your work. <br />Collaborate with free software communities.</h1>
            <p>
                <img src="images/home/main-image.jpg" alt="Collaborate with free software communities." />
            </p>
            <p class="intro-text center">
                <strong>Launchpad is a unique collaboration and hosting platform for free software, available through the web, email and a web services API.</strong></p>
                <p>It brings communities together &mdash; regardless of their choice of tools &mdash; by making it easy to share code, bug reports, translations and ideas across projects.
            </p><br />
            <h2>Choose Launchpad to&#58;</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Encourage contributions to <br />your project.</li>
                <li>Improve collaboration with <br />other projects and developers.</li>
                <li>Build communities using teams <br />and mailing lists.</li>
                <li>Promote and publish your software.</li>
            </ul>

            <div class="clear"></div>
            <div id="link-holder"><a href="https://launchpad.net/+login">Create your Launchpad account &gt;</a><br /><a href="https://launchpad.net/projects/+new-guided">Add your project to Launchpad &gt;</a></div>
        </div>
        <div id="page-intro-bottom"></div>
